---
/**
 * CaseStudies.astro — Proof, Not Promises
 * Two case study cards showcasing real client and own-brand results.
 * Grid layout: details left (60%), results right (40%) on desktop.
 */
---

<section id="results" class="py-24 md:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
    <!-- Section Heading -->
    <h2
      class="mb-16 text-center text-3xl font-bold md:text-4xl"
      style="font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'Fira Code', monospace;"
    >
      <span class="comment-prefix">// </span><span class="gradient-text">Proof, Not Promises</span>
    </h2>

    <!-- Cards Container -->
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-8">

      <!-- Card 1: Retail Client -->
      <div
        class="fade-in-up glass-card overflow-hidden p-8 md:p-10"
      >
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-[3fr_2fr] md:gap-10">
          <!-- Left: Details -->
          <div>
            <!-- Tag -->
            <span
              class="mb-4 inline-block rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-xs"
              style="font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'Fira Code', monospace; background-color: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1); color: #8b5cf6;"
            >
              Client Project
            </span>

            <!-- Title -->
            <h3
              class="mb-4 text-xl font-bold md:text-2xl"
              style="font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'Fira Code', monospace; color: #e6edf3;"
            >
              Traditional Chocolate Shop to E-Commerce Roadmap
            </h3>

            <!-- Challenge -->
            <p
              class="mb-6 leading-relaxed"
              style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; color: #8b949e;"
            >
              New owner, one week into a $537K/year business. Zero e-commerce experience. Working 84+ hours a week. Needed a complete digital transformation plan — fast.
            </p>

            <!-- What I built -->
            <h4
              class="mb-3 text-base font-semibold"
              style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; color: #e6edf3;"
            >
              What I built
            </h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; color: #8b949e;">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="mt-1.5 block h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full" style="background-color: #06b6d4;"></span>
                <span>18 deliverable areas — competitive analysis, pricing strategy, SEO, email, social, UGC, partnerships, financial tracking</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="mt-1.5 block h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full" style="background-color: #06b6d4;"></span>
                <span>Custom Content Creator PRO v5.3 — web app for generating platform-specific AI prompts, handed over running</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="mt-1.5 block h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full" style="background-color: #06b6d4;"></span>
                <span>Corporate gifting program with B2B sales materials — $80K–$300K identified opportunity</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="mt-1.5 block h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full" style="background-color: #06b6d4;"></span>
                <span>Pricing optimization strategy — +$115K annual revenue from margin adjustments alone</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="mt-1.5 block h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full" style="background-color: #06b6d4;"></span>
                <span>Interactive client dashboard deployed on GitHub Pages — live, browser-based, no downloads</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Right: Results -->
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 md:border-l md:pl-10" style="border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);">
            <div>
              <div
                class="text-3xl font-bold"
                style="font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'Fira Code', monospace; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6, #06b6d4); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text;"
              >
                6 Weeks
              </div>
              <div class="text-sm" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; color: #8b949e;">
                Delivery Time
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div
                class="text-3xl font-bold"
                style="font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'Fira Code', monospace; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6, #06b6d4); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text;"
              >
                $115K
              </div>
              <div class="text-sm" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; color: #8b949e;">
                Revenue from Pricing Alone
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div
                class="text-3xl font-bold"
                style="font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'Fira Code', monospace; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6, #06b6d4); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text;"
              >
                $300K
              </div>
              <div class="text-sm" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; color: #8b949e;">
                Corporate Gifting Opportunity
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div
                class="text-3xl font-bold"
                style="font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'Fira Code', monospace; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6, #06b6d4); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text;"
              >
                $1M+
              </div>
              <div class="text-sm" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; color: #8b949e;">
                Revenue Trajectory (from $537K)
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3: Auto Shop — D.JANC Workshop -->
      <div
        class="fade-in-up glass-card overflow-hidden p-8 md:p-10"
      >
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-[3fr_2fr] md:gap-10">
          <!-- Left: Details -->
          <div>
            <!-- Tag -->
            <span
              class="mb-4 inline-block rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-xs"
              style="font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'Fira Code', monospace; background-color: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1); color: #8b5cf6;"
            >
              Client Project
            </span>

            <!-- Title -->
            <h3
              class="mb-4 text-xl font-bold md:text-2xl"
              style="font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'Fira Code', monospace; color: #e6edf3;"
            >
              Auto Repair Shop — Full SEO & AI-Visible Website, Overnight
            </h3>

            <!-- Challenge -->
            <p
              class="mb-6 leading-relaxed"
              style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; color: #8b949e;"
            >
              A traditional automotive workshop with no web presence. Needed a professional site that would rank in local search, appear in Google AI Overviews, and answer the exact questions customers type into ChatGPT and Perplexity.
            </p>

            <!-- What I built -->
            <h4
              class="mb-3 text-base font-semibold"
              style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; color: #e6edf3;"
            >
              What I built
            </h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; color: #8b949e;">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="mt-1.5 block h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full" style="background-color: #06b6d4;"></span>
                <span>15-page Astro website — homepage, 8 service pages, pricing, FAQ, reviews, about, blog hub</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="mt-1.5 block h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full" style="background-color: #06b6d4;"></span>
                <span>Full technical SEO — LocalBusiness + AutoRepair schema, FAQPage JSON-LD on every service page, XML sitemap, canonical URLs, hreflang</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="mt-1.5 block h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full" style="background-color: #06b6d4;"></span>
                <span>LLM optimization — answer-first copy structure, structured pricing tables, 21 FAQ entries with JSON-LD so ChatGPT, Perplexity, and Google AI cite the site directly</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="mt-1.5 block h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full" style="background-color: #06b6d4;"></span>
                <span>Full launch plan — go-live checklist, Google Business Profile setup, local citation strategy</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="mt-1.5 block h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full" style="background-color: #06b6d4;"></span>
                <span>Built overnight by autonomous AI agent from a PRD with 18 user stories — zero manual coding</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Right: Results -->
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 md:border-l md:pl-10" style="border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);">
            <div>
              <div
                class="text-3xl font-bold"
                style="font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'Fira Code', monospace; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6, #06b6d4); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text;"
              >
                1 Night
              </div>
              <div class="text-sm" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; color: #8b949e;">
                Build Time
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div
                class="text-3xl font-bold"
                style="font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'Fira Code', monospace; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6, #06b6d4); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text;"
              >
                15 Pages
              </div>
              <div class="text-sm" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; color: #8b949e;">
                Delivered
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div
                class="text-3xl font-bold"
                style="font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'Fira Code', monospace; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6, #06b6d4); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text;"
              >
                21 FAQs
              </div>
              <div class="text-sm" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; color: #8b949e;">
                JSON-LD Structured
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div
                class="text-3xl font-bold"
                style="font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'Fira Code', monospace; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6, #06b6d4); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text;"
              >
                AI-Ready
              </div>
              <div class="text-sm" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; color: #8b949e;">
                ChatGPT · Perplexity · Google AI
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2: Own Brands (GearTOP + TapeGeeks) -->
      <div
        class="fade-in-up glass-card overflow-hidden p-8 md:p-10"
      >
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-[3fr_2fr] md:gap-10">
          <!-- Left: Details -->
          <div>
            <!-- Tag -->
            <span
              class="mb-4 inline-block rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-xs"
              style="font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'Fira Code', monospace; background-color: rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.1); color: #06b6d4;"
            >
              My Businesses
            </span>

            <!-- Title -->
            <h3
              class="mb-4 text-xl font-bold md:text-2xl"
              style="font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'Fira Code', monospace; color: #e6edf3;"
            >
              Two E-Commerce Brands Running on AI Tools I Built Myself
            </h3>

            <!-- Challenge -->
            <p
              class="mb-6 leading-relaxed"
              style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; color: #8b949e;"
            >
              Two e-commerce brands. $2M+ in ad spend. Paying $75K-$125K annually for agencies, freelancers, and services. Needed to cut costs without cutting results.
            </p>

            <!-- What I built -->
            <h4
              class="mb-3 text-base font-semibold"
              style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; color: #e6edf3;"
            >
              What I built
            </h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; color: #8b949e;">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="mt-1.5 block h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full" style="background-color: #06b6d4;"></span>
                <span>Custom AI content generation systems (100+ product descriptions, brand voice maintained)</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="mt-1.5 block h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full" style="background-color: #06b6d4;"></span>
                <span>Marketing automation workflows replacing manual email, social, and ad management</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="mt-1.5 block h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full" style="background-color: #06b6d4;"></span>
                <span>2 iOS apps (SunUp by GearTOP, RunMate Pro) — built as a non-coder using AI tools</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="mt-1.5 block h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full" style="background-color: #06b6d4;"></span>
                <span>Analytics dashboards aggregating data from Shopify, Amazon, Google, Meta</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="mt-1.5 block h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full" style="background-color: #06b6d4;"></span>
                <span>Operational automation (inventory alerts, reorder triggers, journey orchestration)</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Right: Results -->
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 md:border-l md:pl-10" style="border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);">
            <div>
              <div
                class="text-3xl font-bold"
                style="font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'Fira Code', monospace; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6, #06b6d4); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text;"
              >
                $75K+
              </div>
              <div class="text-sm" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; color: #8b949e;">
                Annual Savings
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div
                class="text-3xl font-bold"
                style="font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'Fira Code', monospace; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6, #06b6d4); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text;"
              >
                5-10x
              </div>
              <div class="text-sm" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; color: #8b949e;">
                Content Volume
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div
                class="text-3xl font-bold"
                style="font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'Fira Code', monospace; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6, #06b6d4); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text;"
              >
                15-20x
              </div>
              <div class="text-sm" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; color: #8b949e;">
                Email Marketing ROI
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div
                class="text-3xl font-bold"
                style="font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'Fira Code', monospace; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6, #06b6d4); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text;"
              >
                2 Apps
              </div>
              <div class="text-sm" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; color: #8b949e;">
                Live in App Store
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
